{"tid":1524450,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急 請全部警二代跟我咁做...","createTime":"2019-08-31T17:16:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T17:23:47.000Z","uid":306337,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6fb2e28248d6588950b2ae71e0698a47e6415435","tid":1524450,"uid":306337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:16:14.000Z","msg":"首先 我會稱各位同自己 係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">狗二代</span></strong> 我地既父母就係狗嚟. 無論佢地既立場係點,中立 <span style=\"color: teal;\">淺藍</span> <span style=\"color: gold;\">黃</span>都好,唔重要,經過呢一夜<span style=\"color: red;\">全警隊都係狗</span><br />\n<br />\n至於要做啲咩...<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1</span><br />\n<br />\n拒絕同佢哋交流, 無論講咩都好, 覆 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">哦</span>  就.真係有咩事,就搵其他屋企人傳達. 如果佢問你點解咁答 就答: <strong><em>你自己諗下啦</em></strong><br />\n<br />\n其二<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔再同枱食飯</span><br />\n<br />\n無論係屋企煮飯,出街一齊食又好, 一律出街食, 唔好同隻狗同枱食飯.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其三<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔獨處</span><br />\n<br />\n如果狗隻放假係屋企,自己出去,有咁耐得咁耐, 或者鎖自己係房, 拒絕同佢見面.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要等佢自己知,佢地自己仔女都同佢哋割蓆,<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一族嘅羞恥</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔會齋講唔做, 我自己都係狗二代, 老母係個垃圾散仔老屎忽交通警,係八鄉警署做.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢刻開始,我唔撚會再理佢</span></span>"},{"pid":"debd54ed99331b456fcd2bcf1638dc6436adbc38","tid":1524450,"uid":91314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:17:59.000Z","msg":"辛苦啦<br />\n小狗狗"},{"pid":"e5236653d82c93371c6dfbdaa9e0706e89696b45","tid":1524450,"uid":308567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:18:13.000Z","msg":"［文宣超新星爆炸］ 魔警阻止人道救援<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMjHJNz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMjHJNz.jpg&h=3027d600&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/110776013598523/posts/125201912155933?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F110776013598523%2Fposts%2F125201912155933%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70vQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=c0e2a07e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/110776013598523/posts/125201912155933?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n好撚唔人道 係咪可以推到班撚樣上軍事法庭<br />\nSorry P牌每日一post 有冇手足幫手開post"},{"pid":"95b5b7c9e2b631d5cc5afd53f2121b0ca6c442c0","tid":1524450,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:19:09.000Z","msg":"狗仔冇資格分黃定中定藍<br />\n正如你都唔會分黑警係黃定藍"},{"pid":"6e90e20e431c58564e5e5f0a6bacc540b9df41b8","tid":1524450,"uid":196087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:19:48.000Z","msg":"不合作到辭職為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"586f6efb783bbd125c180c99ed2ea93cc3579af8","tid":1524450,"uid":306337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"95b5b7c9e2b631d5cc5afd53f2121b0ca6c442c0","tid":1524450,"uid":8308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:19:09.000Z","msg":"狗仔冇資格分黃定中定藍<br />\n正如你都唔會分黑警係黃定藍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:21:40.000Z","msg":"冇錯, 我呢隻狗二代本身就係有罪. 為咗贖罪, 唯有咁做, 由佢地最脆弱既一面瓦解警隊"},{"pid":"17eed1c215fc0da5dfe565b0b6255c6e450c2bf7","tid":1524450,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:22:14.000Z","msg":"good dog<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c449d2e35c1e46d6dd1e7b2cd8d969142b2fd13","tid":1524450,"uid":306337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"debd54ed99331b456fcd2bcf1638dc6436adbc38","tid":1524450,"uid":91314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:17:59.000Z","msg":"辛苦啦<br />\n小狗狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:22:31.000Z","msg":"辛你老母苦, 同出面同我一齊捱生捱死,仲唔介意我係狗仔既手足比 我呢啲算條春"},{"pid":"e712d9ca52ca314ec9a73d3f530474c1cfa69254","tid":1524450,"uid":276365,"li